  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2026 BCIJF Daytime Performances";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/b5c7670b-86e8-4e80-8709-db7642d21edd.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>BC Interior Jazz Festival presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">2026 Daytime Performances</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>The BC Interior Jazz Festival hosts Jazz Band and Vocal Jazz adjudicated performances at the Kelowna Community Theatre on Thursday, Friday and Saturday. The public is welcome to all daily adjudicated performances. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>There is a day pass for KCT performances available to purchase on the KCT box office website as well as in the lobby for $10. Festival participants get in free. A schedule of all group performances is posted on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bcinteriorjazzfestival.com/\">www.bcinteriorjazzfestival.com</a>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">General Seating  $10.00</span>  ($6.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $1.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">BCIJF Daytime Performances</span> tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
