  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2026 BCIJF Student Showcase";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/2b56f712-e00a-4a4d-8074-2d1c870a3b8d.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>BC Interior Jazz Festival presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">2026 STUDENT SHOWCASE CONCERT</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>The best student performers from the festival are invited by adjudicators to return to the stage at the Student Showcase Concert on Saturday night. These supremely talented young musicians are sure to impress and entertain. 7:00 pm on Saturday, April 18th, 2026 at the Kelowna Community Theatre.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular $25.36</span> ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">BCIJF Student Showcase Concert</span> tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
