<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/360201ARKDLVNMRPDGSMVMVQHBRTVJNSM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Alan Doyle Touchdown Kickoff Concert";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/61f520ba-816b-4b17-9093-a765a25b3ebf.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>BCLC presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">ALAN DOYLE</span></h1><h2>TOUCHDOWN KELOWNA KICKOFF CONCERT</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Let’s kick off <span class=\"BoldText\">Touchdown Kelowna’s</span> opening weekend with a high-energy headline performance built for big crowds and bigger moments. We’ve got the sunshine, we’ve got the scenery… now all we need is a proper kitchen party.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>And on June 26, <span class=\"BoldText\">Alan Doyle</span> (<span class=\"ItalicText\">Great Big Sea</span>) is bringing exactly that to kick things off in style.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s your <span class=\"BoldText\">Kickoff Concert</span> - and they’re going to raise the roof, the tent, and maybe a glass or two while they’re at it.  So bring your friends, bring your voices-and they’ll bring the songs.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Kelowna, let’s get this party started.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Additional Information:</span><span><br/></span><ul><li> This is an all-ages event</li><li> Gates open at 7:30pm</li><li> All tickets are lawn seating.  You are encouraged to bring your own folding chair or blanket.</li><li> Full site liquor license in effect. Food trucks and beverage service available on site.</li></ul><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><ul><li><span class=\"BoldText\">General Admission  $72.45</span>  ($63.00 base price + $9.45 service charge)</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP Admission*  $144.90</span>  ($126.00 base price + $18.90 service charge)</li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Concert Bundle Offer:</span><span><br/></span>Planning to hit both headline concerts? You’re in luck. Purchase tickets to the Kickoff Concert and Boots on the Beach and receive a discounted bundle rate automatically at checkout.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li>General Admission Kickoff + General Admission Boots on the Beach = <span class=\"BoldText\">$21.00 savings</span></li><li>VIP* Kickoff + VIP* Boots on the Beach = <span class=\"BoldText\">$42.00 savings</span></li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Ticket types must match. Discount applies automatically at checkout, no promo code needed.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">*VIP Tickets include special VIP area with a private bar and washrooms.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">The event will proceed rain or shine.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Tickets for <span class=\"BoldText\">Alan Doyle Touchdown Kickoff Concert</span> and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
