  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Anne of Green Gables";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/bbbfcc5c-3c39-44b6-82d2-b00e47fc6578.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>New Vintage Theatre presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">ANNE OF GREEN GABLES</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>New Vintage Theatre is thrilled to bring this Canadian classic about a red-headed orphan longing for a home of her own to the stage as our annual holiday play. It will be a wonderful, all ages celebration of the season featuring a cast of incredible local talent.  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $42.96</span>  ($35.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.60 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student/Senior  $37.21</span>  ($30.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.85 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child  $31.46</span>  ($25.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Anne of Green Gables</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
