<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/333001APGGVKPSNGJRMLJGDDLHJDRTLLD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Arrival & Dreams";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/e31b0d92-5d00-4f4d-a2ea-6a04517a1917.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Sonic Flower Entertainment presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">ARRIVAL & DREAMS</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Canada's Ultimate Tribute to ABBA and Fleetwood Mac</span></span> </h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">ARRIVAL</span></span>, Canada's Tribute to ABBA delivers an authentic, high energy tribute to one of the greatest pop bands of all time!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This dynamic six piece group performs in dazzling costumes, capturing the style, spirit and unmistakeable sound of ABBA with incredible accuracy.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For over 20 years, <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">ARRIVAL</span></span> has been packing venues across North America and beyond, performing hundreds of shows at casinos, theatres, festivals and corporate events worldwide -- from Las Vegas and the Dominican Republic, Oregon, Washington and Illinois in the USA to all of the major cities across Canada from East to West!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Audiences are amazed at how true <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">ARRIVAL</span></span> sounds to the original ABBA and their vibrant choreography & stage presence take the experience to another level!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Relive the magic, the music and the memories of ABBA with<span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">ARRIVAL</span></span> - Canada's Tribute to ABBA! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rbeAcxvncx0\">Arrival - Canada&#39;s Tribute to Abba Video</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">DREAMS</span></span> the Ultimate Tribute to Fleetwood Mac is indeed the ultimate Fleetwood Mac experience!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The group is an authentic six piece tribute that captures the look, sound & spirit of the legendary band!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Performing in stunning costumes inspired by the originals, <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">DREAMS</span></span> brings Fleetwood Mac's timeless hits to life with world class musicianship, incredible harmonies and captivating stage presence!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For over 20 years this talented group has performed hundreds of shows from the Dominican Republic, Las Vegas, Chicago, towns in Oregon, Washington and all of the major cities from East to West in Canada!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Audiences are amazed at how close <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">DREAMS</span></span> looks and sounds to the real thing!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If you're looking for one of the most captivating and professional tribute acts out there, book <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">DREAMS</span></span> and relive the magic of Fleetwood Mac all over again!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mUMfySA0CUY\">Dreams - Canada&#39;s Ultimate Tribute to Fleetwood Mac Video</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $65.96</span> ($55.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.60 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Arrival & Dreams</span> tickets and their applicable ticket fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
