	</table><span><br/></span>Wentworth Music is proud to present - Big Shiny Tunes Kelowna! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">1 Day - 2 Separate Shows - 30 Total Songs</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">(For the best musical experience buy a 2 show package and make a whole day out of it!)</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come out and support the future of music here in Kelowna as our best and brightest will perform 2 completely different shows Friday June 26th at the Kelowna Community Theatre! Please be sure to get tickets to the correct show your child will be apart of and cheer all the kids on as they perform some of the best Alternative Rock songs from the 80's Late 90's and early 00's. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Important:</span></span> <span class=\"ItalicText\">The two shows on this date are separate events with different content. Please ensure you are selecting tickets for your intended performance.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">7PM SHOW SETLIST</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li>ANIMAL I HAVE BECOME - Three Days Grace</li><li>MISS MURDER - AFI</li><li>SONG 2 - Blur</li><li>HELENA - MY CHEMICAL ROMANCE</li><li>ONLY HAPPY WHEN IT RAINS - Garbage</li><li>GIRLS & BOYS - Blur</li><li>SWING, SWING - The All-American Rejects</li><li>KRYPTONITE - 3 Doors Down</li><li>MODERN LOVE - David Bowie</li><li>HERO - Chad Kroeger/Josey Scott</li><li>TEENAGE DIRTBAG - Wheatus</li><li>EVERYBODY'S FOOL - Evanescence</li><li>ENJOY THE SILENCE - Depeche Mode</li><li>CLOSING TIME - Semisonic</li></ul><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $32.55</span>  ($26.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.94 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span>