<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/363201AGRKJJJHHRRLKKCNVLNMQVCLNQT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CMK - Busch Trio";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/8e851ba8-a213-4ae4-94c4-10c5f18ef29c.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Chamber Music Kelowna presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">BUSCH TRIO</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Their artistic identity was shaped early on when violinist Mathieu van Bellen began performing on the historic 1783 G.B. Guadagnini “ex-Adolf Busch,” inspiring the trio’s admiration for early-twentieth-century chamber traditions, reflected also in their choice to perform on gut strings. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Praised by critics for their “effortless musicianship” and captivating ensemble playing, they appear regularly at leading festivals and concert halls across Europe and North America. Their celebrated recordings for Alpha Classics, including works by Dvořák, Schubert, Ravel, and Shostakovich, have further established their reputation. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $67.50</span>  ($56.34 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.80 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student (w/ID)  $25.00</span>  ($19.38 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.26 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Busch Trio</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
