<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/235801ANNNHTLQPVBSCBNJTPPMNNPDJPV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CMK 25/26 - Balourdet Quartet";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/16b87127-d2ec-4201-b79e-ba44bade57db.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Chamber Music Kelowna presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">BALOURDET QUARTET</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Balourdet Quartet is a prize-winning and passionate ensemble. Recently awarded a 2024 Avery Fisher Career Grant, the ensemble is quickly becoming one of classical music’s hottest tickets. The Quartet stands out for its vibrant energy and masterful blend of technical precision and emotional depth that brings fresh perspectives to both beloved classics and modern compositions.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Presented by: <span class=\"BoldText\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://chambermusickelowna.ca/\">Chamber Music Kelowna</a></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult: $65.00</span> ($54.44 + $2.36 CIF + $8.20 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student (with ID): $25.00</span> ($19.65 + $2.36 CIF + $2.99 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.10 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Chamber Music Kelowna <span class=\"BoldText\">Balourdet Quartet</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
