<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/317201APPTLRCLDMKPHCJBTRCTQVJKLPC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Creedence Clearwater Relived - Bad Moon Riders CCR Tribute Concert";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/64fe7ddc-977d-4607-a7f8-2c9b813a1d83.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>BMR Entertainment Ltd. presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">CREEDENCE CLEARWATER RELIVED</span></h1><h2>Bad Moon Riders CCR Tribute Concert</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>CREEDENCE CLEARWATER RELIVED - Bad Moon Riders CCR Tribute Concert returns to the Rotary Centre for the Arts for a night of Creedence Clearwater revival! The Bad Moon Riders bring the hits of Creedence to life in an unforgettable tribute concert. Members of BTO and the Headpins deliver ALL the hits All Nite long in this epic event celebrating the music of one of the greatest bands of all time. Grab your tickets now!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Pricing</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $49.95</span>  ($41.38 base price + $2.36 CIF  + $6.21 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Creedence Clearwater Relived -Bad Moon Riders CCR Tribute Concert</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
