<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/356602ATNJLGHNRVLHCRVGLQDGTLTLTJJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Disney’s Aladdin Jr.";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/7e068f2f-f755-4e0f-8488-a7891399f641.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>St. Joseph Elementary School presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">DISNEY'S ALADDIN JR.</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Disney's Aladdin Jr brings the famous movie to life, on stage. In Agrabah, City of Enchantment, every beggar has a story and every camel has a tail! Aladdin, a kind but wily, street urchin, falls in love with beautiful Princess Jasmine, who he knows is waaaaay out of his league. It just so happens, however, that the Sultan has declared Princess Jasmine must choose a husband within the next day. After she turns down the offers from various wealthy suitors, Aladdin -- with the help of a fast-talking, magical Genie -- introduces himself as wealthy suitor, Prince Ali of Ababwa. Meanwhile, evil royal advisor, Jafar, also has his sights set on the kingdom, and tries to convince the Sultan to force Jasmine to wed him. Will love conquer all? Perhaps - if love has a little help from a Genie.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee. <span class=\"BoldText\">Disney’s Aladdin Jr.</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-13T12:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
