<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/360801AJTKRDCBJLBLRLHMPGJTGHNTVVH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Flip Flop Gala";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/60ff8dfb-ba55-4fd7-95d0-fdf1aa2df778.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Touchdown Kelowna presents</h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">FLIP FLOP GALA</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Where Black Tie Meets Barefoot.</span><span><br/></span>An exclusive <span class=\"UnderlineText\">19+</span>, elevated Okanagan experience unlike anything the region has seen<span><br/></span>before.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">The Experience</span><span><br/></span>The Flip Flop Gala is an exclusive, high-end ticketed celebration staged right in front of the Waterfront performance stage — placing you at the center of the spotlight.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From the moment guests arrive, the tone is clear: this is not your typical gala.<span><br/></span><ul><li>Men in tuxedos.</li><li>Women in sequins and silk.</li><li>And beneath the elegance? Flip flops. Bare feet. Sandals.</li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Formal on top. Beach on the bottom.</span><span><br/></span>It’s refined irreverence.  Elevated but unbuttoned.  Sophisticated with a wink.  High-energy but intimate.  Effortlessly cool.  Proudly local.  Unexpected and buzz-worthy!<span><br/></span>As DJ Pri builds the night’s soundtrack, party lighting pulses across the stage. Player, Mascot and cheer appearances inject surprise moments of hometown pride. Local celebrities mingle naturally within the crowd — no VIP barriers, just elevated accessibility. Bespoke “Cabana” lounge seating and a dance floor satisfy guests’ desires.  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get your people together and get your tickets here before they’re gone!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Additional Information:</span><span><br/></span><ul><li> This is a 19+ event</li><li> Gates open at 6:00pm</li><li> Themed attire encouraged</li><li> Tickets include a welcome cocktail, food grazing stations and a no-host bar.</li><li> Limited tickets available.</li><li> Event happens rain or shine</li></ul>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">General  $181.13</span>  ($157.75 base price + $23.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Flip Flop Gala</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-29T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/60ff8dfb-ba55-4fd7-95d0-fdf1aa2df778.jpg>;
