<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/368401ALRPBVGTJVLBTCBCQGHNRRNVSNB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "KCCB - North American Soundscapes";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/1437e595-a24f-4bce-89c6-346cfb18a306.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Kelowna City Concert Band presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">NORTH AMERICAN SOUNDSCAPES</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Under the direction of our talented conductor Robert Payne, the Kelowna City Concert Band presents North American Soundscapes - a musical journey across the continent featuring beloved selections such as Shenandoah, Red River Valley, Prairie Songs.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With a proud history dating back to 1894, the Kelowna City Concert Band has been a cornerstone of Kelowna's cultural community for over 130 years, bringing together musicians of all ages who share a passion for music and community.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $25.00</span>  ($21.25 base price + $3.75 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior  $20.00</span>  ($17.00 base price + $3.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student $12.00</span>  ($9.37 base price + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Kids 12 years and under are free</span> - no ticket is necessary.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All above prices include GST.
<span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">North American Soundscapes</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
