  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Kelowna Ribfest";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/a2350fd9-0bd7-45a0-851a-b572bc130959.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Impact Events present</h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">KELOWNA RIBFEST</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Avoid lineups pre-purchase your entry to Kelowna Ribfest!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>2026 brings back this popular family festival. This three-day event will be packed with mouthwatering rib competitions, live music, and a ton of family fun!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Enjoy top rib chefs battling it out in City Park, live music to keep you dancing, a dedicated kids zone, family activities, an artisan marketplace and much more. From diverse flavours, vegan options to engaging entertainment, there is something for everyone.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss out on being at this much-anticipated festival.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Additional Information:</span><span><br/></span><ul><li> Each ticket is valid for <span class=\"BoldText\">single‑day admission</span> to Kelowna Ribfest, held July 3–5, 2026.</li><li> Admission is <span class=\"BoldText\">free for children 12 and under.</span></li><li> When purchasing, please select the date you are most likely to attend. Tickets may be redeemed <span class=\"BoldText\">ON ANY ONE</span> of the three event days.</li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Ribfest Hours:</span> <span><br/></span><ul><li>Friday, July 3: 2 pm – 9 pm </li><li>Saturday, July 4: 11 am – 9 pm </li><li>Sunday, July 5: 11 am – 7 pm </li></ul><span class=\"ItalicText\">Tickets may be redeemed on any <span class=\"BoldText\">ONE</span> of the three days.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $3.00</span>  ($2.73 base price + $0.27 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child 12 and under - free admission</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Tickets for <span class=\"BoldText\">Ribfest 2026</span> and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
