<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/284001AHJSCVQLCTCJKVNRPGJSNKDBBLC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Legendary Rock Live!";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/799a995b-8baa-40ac-9375-4516a089d009.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>The Gary Cable Foundation presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">LEGENDARY ROCK LIVE!</span>  </h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><h2>featuring The Gary Cable Project</h2><span><br/></span>Back by popular demand! The Gary Cable Project makes its return to the Kelowna Community Theatre with Legendary Rock Live! The 'Project returns to the Okanagan with its world-class horn section, to perform some of the greatest music ever made -- Chicago, Blood Sweat & Tears, Steely Dan, Supertramp, Tina Turner, Toto, Lighthouse, Three Dog Night -- and more! Don't miss this unforgettable night of \"Legendary Music by Legendary Musicians\"!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Comprised of Canada’s top live and session players, The Gary Cable Project is a 9-piece band including full horn section; an All-Star group of musicians who have recorded and performed and toured with the legends — Barbra Streisand, Bryan Adams, Aerosmith, Chilliwack, the Pointer Sisters, Sarah McLachlan, David Foster, the Powder Blues, Stuart Copeland (the Police), David Clayton-Thomas/Blood Sweat and Tears, Long John Baldry, Jann Arden, Colin James, Gino Vanelli, Michael Bublé — to name a few. You do not want to miss the Tour!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All proceeds benefit The Central Okanagan Foundation.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For more information: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.garycableproject.com/\">www.garycableproject.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Pricing</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $71.36</span>  ($60.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior  $65.61</span>  ($55.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.25 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student  $36.86</span>  ($30.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">First Two Rows  $36.86</span>  ($30.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Legendary Rock Live!</span> Tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
