<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/202601AMDSTNTJSMPHMCHVJGLVDHPQMRB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Let's Go Surfin'! - A Musical Salute to the Beach Boys";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/9db1165b-d700-4a68-8f3b-9eae136a8a62.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>BackBeat Entertainment presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">LET'S GO SURFIN'!</span> </h1><h2>A Musical Salute to the Beach Boys</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready to be swept away by the timeless melodies of the Beach Boys! Join us for a nostalgic evening filled with their iconic hits and concert favorites. Let's Go Surfin'! is performed by BACKBEAT, Canada's most authentic musical tribute to the 60's. They nail the incredibly intricate Beach Boys harmonies perfectly! All the genius of Brian Wilson's songwriting and studio wizardry blossoms on stage in a spectacular musical salute to one of the greatest pop groups of all time!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All the hits are here! From the energetic \"Fun, Fun, Fun\" and \"Surfin' USA\" to the emotional masterpieces like \"Don't Worry, Baby\" and \"God Only Knows\", this show will take you on a musical journey through the sunshine-soaked sounds of California. Feel the sand between your toes and the warmth of the summer sun on your face as you sing along to your favourite Beach Boys classics.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don't miss this unforgettable opportunity to relive the music and the magic of The Beach Boys. in a spectacular tribute of both sight and sound.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://youtu.be/rsQyrEt7zIU\">Let&#39;s Go Surfin&#39;! - Theatre Promo</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">More Information</span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.backbeatentertainment.ca/let-s-go-surfin\">BackBeat Entertainment - Let&#39;s Go Surfin&#39;!</a><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100063264905641\">BackBeat Entertainment Facebook</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Pricing</span></h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular: $49.95</span> ($41.08 + $2.36 CIF + $6.51 Service Fee)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Let's Go Surfin'!</span> ticket prices and service fees for this event are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
