			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/c98e9720-cf04-4019-b77b-d0b7f47c1fac.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Dolyna Ukrainian Cultural Society presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">LETTERS FROM HOME</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Join Dolyna Ukrainian Dancers for their year-end performance, Letters From Home - a moving Ukrainian dance production that brings together dancers of all ages in a powerful story of memory, identity, and the pull of home.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $31.46</span>  ($25.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child under 12  $19.99</span>  ($15.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Letters From Home</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
