  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Music Fest MS";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Klick Entertainment presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">MUSIC FEST MS</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"Music Fest MS\" is a charity fundraiser in support of Multiple Sclerosis. Tickets and donations are given to MS Canada to support research initiatives to find a cure for MS. To date, this show has raised over $170,000. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This unique event features a \"Nashville Songwriters Round\" where professional artists and songwriters share the stories behind their songs. You'll hear #1 hits played on the radio, songs that have been put on hold by major artists, and songs from local performers around the Okanagan valley. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Fight. Play. Feel. Live. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Be a part of the growing community and support group, and let's put an end to Multiple Sclerosis.
""";
