<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/272401ASSJSQCTBDCBHGMHVMGBJLJHSPV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "OSO 6 - Surprise! (Kelowna)";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/b148ac3a-439f-4fca-964f-d02d4745ca4a.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Okanagan Symphony Orchestra presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">SURPRISE!</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\"> featuring Heather Beaty, flute</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Expect the unexpected! From a bizarre battle to a fiery flute concerto to Don Juan’s descent into Hell, this eclectic program spans centuries of creativity. Principal flutist Heather Beaty makes her solo debut, while Caroline Shaw’s Haydn-inspired dreamscape is juxtaposed with his famous “Surprise” Symphony No. 94.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Check out a curated playlist for this concert <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLqvczKPMSXUQXum-g7sXyu2bC2xv0A5u_\">HERE</a></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Zone A</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $70.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $9.45 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$81.55</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $52.50 base price + $2.10 CIF + $8.40 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$63.00</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Zone B</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $60.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $8.40 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$70.55</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $45.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $7.35 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$54.45</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $15.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $4.20 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$21.30</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Zone C</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $35.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $7.35 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$44.45</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $35.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $7.35 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$44.45</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $15.00 base price + $2.10  CIF + $4.20 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$21.30</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Senior - age 65+, Youth - up to age 24.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.00 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Okanagan Symphony Orchestra <span class=\"BoldText\">Surprise!</span> tickets and applicable fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
