			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/c7f6eb2b-3ad9-4179-a703-76c41e665aed.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Okanagan Symphony Orchestra presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">BEETHOVEN'S FIFTH</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\"> featuring the Symphony's Chorus.</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Experience the symphony that changed music forever. Shocking at the time of its premiere with its emotional intensity, today Beethoven’s Fifth is one of the world’s most recognizable works of art. After more than a decade, the Okanagan Symphony Orchestra returns to this iconic masterpiece to close the season with this monument of musical expression. This concert also features the Symphony's Chorus in Ola Gjeilo’s Sunrise Mass, a profound and expressive journey, full of soaring melodies and walls of sonic power.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Check out a curated playlist for this concert <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLqvczKPMSXUSztznv-K5aiOktyt_uFln5\">HERE</a></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Zone A</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $70.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $9.45 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$81.55</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $52.50 base price + $2.10 CIF + $8.40 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$63.00</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Zone B</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $60.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $8.40 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$70.55</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $45.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $7.35 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$54.45</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $15.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $4.20 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$21.30</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Zone C</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $35.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $7.35 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$44.45</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $35.00 base price + $2.10 CIF + $7.35 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$44.45</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $15.00 base price + $2.10  CIF + $4.20 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$21.30</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Senior - age 65yrs+, Youth - up to age 24yrs.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.00 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Okanagan Symphony Orchestra <span class=\"BoldText\">Beethoven's Fifth</span> tickets and applicable fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
