different than hearing the recorded songs at home. While babies are welcome, they may not enjoy a loud concert singalong. Also, please keep in mind that the ticket policy of a theatre is that every person needs a ticket.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP  $157.04</span> ($134.50 base price + $2.36 CIF + $20.18 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">VIP includes a post-show meet and greet with Raffi. Please stay in your seat after the show for the meet and greet.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1  $82.86</span>  ($70.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2  $59.86</span>  ($50.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $7.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Raffi</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
