  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Relive the Music: 50s, 60s & 70s Show";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/48cfa567-de82-4e01-9dba-f7a61e72e4d5.jpeg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Simply The Best Talent presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">RELIVE THE MUSIC</span></h1><h2>50s, 60s & 70s Show</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Audience Advisory: use of haze.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Back by popular demand - Relive the Music 50s & 60s SHOW is back after 158 standing ovations in a row across Canada with a new twist.  We are keeping the biggest hits from the 50s & 60s, plus adding 70s Disco Mania with new costumes and great entertainment like usual.  Medleys from the Disco era: to name a few - The Village People, Earth Wind & Fire, Bee Gees, Abba, Gloria Gaynor, Chic, Tramps, KC & the Sunshine Band, Sister Sledge and more. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>World champion, as seen twice on Oprah and the Ellen Show, Luisa Marshall will be performing all her magic alongside the other talented singers and the great band. Don’t miss this show.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP (premium seats) $79.00</span>  ($66.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult (19+)  $69.00</span>  ($57.95 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.69 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth (18 and under) $49.00</span>  ($40.56 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.08 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Relive the Music: 50s, 60s & 70s Show</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
