<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/317401AVRJVKCKPJPJDHNLTKQGMPSNTBR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Kelowna Rock Choir";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/d706ea7b-d461-46ed-9d63-832d799d5e7a.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THE KELOWNA ROCK CHOIR</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This show is SOLD OUT! <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/waitlist\">Click here to join the waitlist</a></span>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready to rock with The Kelowna Rock Choir for another unforgettable show, featuring the music of Heart, CCR, AC/DC, Blink 182, Talking Heads, and more!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This isn’t just any choir performance – backed by a live band, they’ll deliver classic rock anthems with the raw energy and excitement of a full-blown rock show. Feel the powerful vocals and infectious rhythms that will have you singing along and dancing in your seat. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you’re a die-hard classic rock fan or just looking for a fun night out, this concert promises something for everyone.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All proceeds will support Central Okanagan Food Bank, so bring your family, friends, and your best rock ‘n’ roll spirit for a night of music, community, and celebration!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss your chance to experience the thrill of a live rock show with one of the largest and most spirited choirs in town. Join us for an evening that will leave you buzzing long after the final note – grab your tickets now!​<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://nicklariviere.com/kelowna/\">www.kelownarockchoir.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $30.00</span>  ($24.04 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.60 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Kelowna Rock Choir</span>  tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
