<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/360401ARNRPTTVJQMRCMSMPMVGMTVQKJM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Road Hammers Boots on the Beach Concert";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/eb344a16-2ac3-4619-9e9c-d68263b4998b.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Leavitt Machinery presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THE ROAD HAMMERS</span></h1><h2>TOUCHDOWN KELOWNA BOOTS ON THE BEACH CONCERT</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Kelowna… are you ready to turn the beach into a full-throttle country rock party?<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for an unforgettable, full-production performance by The Road Hammers designed to close out the festival at maximum volume. Thousands of fans. Waterfront stage. Summer air. Stadium sound.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Road Hammers are bringing the horsepower to the shoreline.<span><br/></span>Cold drinks, hot sand, and loud guitars-just the way summer should be.<span><br/></span>So grab your crew, lace up your boots-and meet us on the beach!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Kelowna, let’s make this one a night to remember.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Additional Information:</span><span><br/></span><ul><li> This is an all-ages event</li><li> Gates open at 7:30pm</li><li> All tickets are lawn seating.  You are encouraged to bring your own folding chair or blanket.</li><li> Full site liquor license in effect. Food trucks and beverage service available on site.</li></ul><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><ul><li><span class=\"BoldText\">General Admission  $72.45</span>  ($63.00 base price + $9.45 service charge)</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP Admission  $144.90</span>  ($126.00 base price + $18.90 service charge)</li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Concert Bundle Offer:</span><span><br/></span>Planning to hit both headline concerts? You’re in luck. Purchase tickets to the Kickoff Concert and Boots on the Beach and receive a discounted bundle rate automatically at checkout.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li>General Admission Kickoff + General Admission Boots on the Beach = <span class=\"BoldText\">$21.00 savings</span></li><li>VIP* Kickoff + VIP* Boots on the Beach = <span class=\"BoldText\">$42.00 savings</span></li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Ticket types must match. Discount applies automatically at checkout, no promo code needed.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">*VIP Tickets include special VIP area with a private bar and washrooms.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">The event will proceed rain or shine.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Tickets for <span class=\"BoldText\">THE ROAD HAMMERS BOOTS ON THE BEACH CONCERT</span> and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
