<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/331401ALQMPQMMBHRQDKDLSNHRHJHMHDB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Trent McClellan";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/9926ca59-9cbe-45d8-90db-2ee4d11b76e1.jpeg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Dirt Road Kid Productions presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">TRENT McCLELLAN</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">The Be Nice Tour</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Trent McClellan, stand-up veteran, star of This Hour Has 22 Minutes, and host of the Halifax Comedy Fest, is touring Canada with The Be Nice Tour, a brand new hour of material. Fresh off the success of last year’s special <span class=\"ItalicText\">Worry Muffins</span>, Trent returns with new stories, sharp observations, and the signature warmth that has made him one of the country’s most beloved comedians.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $60.00</span>  ($49.81 base price + $2.36 CIF + $7.83 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Trent McClellan</span> applicable ticket fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
