<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/364402ALNMJHHBQVLBBLDJJNBSVSGHBQJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "UNbecoming Film Premiere & Activation";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/e9d26d62-46f0-404e-8c95-73a878ce6acb.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>UN Presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">UNBECOMING</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Film Premiere & Activation</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>A Night Of Truth & Transformation - Kelowna’s Community Event Of The Season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The international premiere of UNbecoming, a groundbreaking documentary film exploring the journey to the truest version of oneself.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Most of life is spent adding layers - titles, possessions, expectations. But the “Inner Knock” reminds us that true power isn’t about adding more; it’s about shedding everything that isn’t you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>UNbecoming follows the journey of stripping away the false self to reveal the essence underneath. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s a film for the person who knows there is more, not out there, but in here. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for a night of film, dialogue and connection.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We are not Becoming.<span><br/></span>We are UNbecoming.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Purchased in March or April:  $15.00</span>  ($8.37 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.91 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Purchased in May:  $20.00</span>  ($13.73 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.91 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Purchased within a week of the show:  $30.00</span>  ($23.73 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.91 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">UNbecoming</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
