		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/f237c7d1-9f19-46fd-84bf-dd6ac52fd76f.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Murray & Peter present </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">WAR ON THE CATWALK</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This show is SOLD OUT! <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/waitlist\">Click here to join the waitlist.</a></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Murray & Peter proudly present the return of, WAR On The Catwalk featuring contestants who appeared on the Emmy-Award winning television show, RuPaul’s Drag Race and Canada’s Drag Race.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Hosted by Alyssa Edwards (winner of RuPaul’s Drag Race Global All Stars 2024), the Canadian tour includes performances by… Jewels Sparkles, Suzie Toot and Lexi from Drag Race Season 17, plus Bosco, Lydia B. Kollins and Daya Betty from All Stars Season 10.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss the Meet & Greet! Fans will enjoy an exclusive photo opportunity with the full cast, receive an official tour fan and souvenir laminate, and get early access to merch that the queens can personally sign. Experience a high-energy, unforgettable night you won’t want to miss!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Limited VIP MEET & GREET EXPERIENCE ADD-ONS are available! Select during checkout process.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1  $158.13</span>  ($135.45 base price + $2.36 CIF + $20.32 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2  $92.92</span>  ($78.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $11.81 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 3  $74.81</span>  ($63.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.45 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">WAR On The Catwalk</span> tickets and fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
