  schema:name "WAR on the Catwalk Meet & Greet Add-On";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/df4d306d-59a2-4ae1-92d9-c52eac02bb9b.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Murray & Peter present </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">WAR ON THE CATWALK</span></h1><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Meet & Greet Experience ADD-ON</span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Get in on the Meet & Greet Experience with WAR On The Catwalk!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This exclusive ADD-ON package is your all-access pass to WAR On The Catwalk like never before.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Here's what you'll receive:<span><br/></span>• Exclusive photo opportunity with the entire cast on the main stage before the show<span><br/></span>• Souvenir laminate with lanyard<span><br/></span>• Office tour clack fan<span><br/></span>• Early access to purchase tour merch (the queens will autograph any of their own merch purchased at the theatre).<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please note:<span><br/></span>• This package <span class=\"BoldText\">does not include a show ticket</span> – tickets must be purchased separately.<span><br/></span>• VIP experience runs approximately from 6:00pm to 7:00pm. Please arrive by <span class=\"BoldText\">5:45pm.</span><span><br/></span>• <span class=\"BoldText\">No refunds or transfers</span> (unless the event is cancelled).<span><br/></span>• Packages are extremely limited, don't miss out!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Important info:<span><br/></span>• All purchasers must have an email address attached to their order or profile so we can communicate updates. We’re not responsible for missed events if we can’t reach you.<span><br/></span>• A representative from the WAR On The Catwalk team will meet you at the main venue entrance to check you in. Please have valid photo ID ready.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Items and timing subject to change.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">$119.54</span>  ($103.95 base price + $15.59 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">WAR On The Catwalk Meet & Greet Experience</span> tickets are not transferrable or refundable.</span>
""";
