  schema:name "WNBF Kelowna Naturals";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/2b6a1398-e605-4d43-bbf1-b9a2cfcec116.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>WNBF Kelowna Naturals presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">WNBF KELOWNA NATURALS</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>The WNBF Kelowna Naturals Bodybuilding Championships is a full-day natural bodybuilding competition showcasing athletes from across British Columbia and beyond. Competitors will take the stage in multiple divisions including Bikini, Figure, Wellness, Fit Body, Men’s Physique, Classic Physique, and Bodybuilding.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This event highlights athletes who compete under strict drug-tested standards, celebrating discipline, health, and performance in natural bodybuilding. Spectators can expect an exciting and energetic atmosphere, inspiring transformations, and high-level competition throughout the day.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Pricing</span></h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Trainer's Pass  $117.71</span>  ($100.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $15.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $60.21</span>  ($50.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $7.85 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child (under 16)  $31.46</span>  ($25.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child (under 5) <span class=\"ItalicText\">free admission</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">WNBF Kelowna Naturals</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
